query:
/*+  */ select count(*)
from question AS q
inner join tag_question AS tq
on tq.question_id = q.id AND q.view_count >= 10 AND q.view_count <= 1000
inner join site AS s
on tq.site_id = s.site_id AND q.site_id = s.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('stackoverflow')
inner join tag AS t
on tq.tag_id = t.id AND t.site_id = s.site_id AND t.name IN ('activerecord',
'android-webview',
'angular6',
'apache-flink',
'arrays',
'cakephp-3.0',
'geolocation',
'google-cloud-firestore',
'listener',
'selenium-webdriver',
'servicestack',
'time',
'xslt-2.0');
